Field Documentation

vpsissIpipeifModule_t vpsissIpipeifCtrl::module

ID of the module to be configured.

vpsissIpipeifDeCompandInsts_t* vpsissIpipeifCtrl::pCompDecompCfg

Pointer to Companding and Decompanding Configuration

vpsissIpipeifDpcCfg_t* vpsissIpipeifCtrl::pDpcCfg

DPC configuration, pointer to array of size 2. Location 0 holds config for vport/isif input Location 1 holds config for memory input. CAUTION DPC on vport & isif is same. Depending on the WDR input DPC is either active on vport or isif lane.

vpsissIpipeifLutConfig_t* vpsissIpipeifCtrl::pLutCfg

Pointer to structure containing Companding and Decompanding Look up Tables, Used for updating these tables only used when module is set to VPS_ISS_IPIPEIF_MODULE_UPDATE_LUT

vpsissIpipeifSaturaInsts_t* vpsissIpipeifCtrl::pSatCfg

Saturation configuration for the VPort, Memory and ISIF input paths

vpsissIpipeifWdrCfg_t* vpsissIpipeifCtrl::pWdrCfg

Pointer to WDR configuration, also used for enabling/disabling WDR
